608//
609// This function runs approximately 200+ns on the 96MHz clock
610//
611// That results in the steps being 1us/32 ~= 31.25ns per step (96MHz Clock)
612// 1us/64 ~= 15.625ns per step (192MHz clock)
613//
614
615//*****************************************************************************
625//*****************************************************************************
626
627#if (defined (__ARMCC_VERSION)) && (__ARMCC_VERSION < 6000000)
628extern __asm void APS25616N_tXPHS_delay( uint32_t ui32Iterations );
629#elif (defined (__ARMCC_VERSION)) && (__ARMCC_VERSION >= 6000000)
630extern __attribute__((always_inline)) void APS25616N_tXPHS_delay( uint32_t ui32Iterations );
631#elif defined(__GNUC_STDC_INLINE__)
632extern void APS25616N_tXPHS_delay( uint32_t ui32Iterations );
633#elif defined(__IAR_SYSTEMS_ICC__)
634#pragma diag_suppress = Pe940 // Suppress IAR compiler warning about missing
635 // return statement on a non-void function
636extern __stackless inline void APS25616N_tXPHS_delay( uint32_t ui32Iterations );
637#pragma diag_default = Pe940 // Restore IAR compiler warning
638#else
639#error Compiler is unknown, please contact Ambiq support team
640#endif
